# Kid privacy + media (plan.md §4.3) — tests/test_repo_files.py asserts each pattern below exists.
# Raw audio/video (phone formats included) and the WHOLE per-episode capture dir (transcript
# included) never reach the public repo.
media/
private/
clips/
*.mp4
*.mov
*.wav
*.m4a
*.mp3
*.ogg
*.m4v
*.3gp
episodes/*/capture/
episodes/*/project/.repair/

